  "content": {
    "prompt": "Construct a program that increments all elements of the array by 1.",
    "source_code": "public class JArrayIncrementElements {\n\tpublic static void main(String[] args) {\n\t\t//Step 1: Define and initialize the array\n\t   int[] lst = { 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6 };\n\t   //Step 2: Iterate through the array elements \n\t   for (int i = 0; i < lst.length; i++) {\n\t\t    //Step 2.1: Increment the element at index i by 1\n\t      lst[i] += 1;\n\t   }\n\t\t//Step 3: Print the array elements\n\t   for (int x : lst) {\n\t\t   System.out.print(x + \"  \");\n\t   }\n\t}\n}"
